    var item = {
        &quot;id&quot;: &quot;00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000&quot;,
        &quot;value&quot;: 1 /* FirstValue */
    };

and if you want to skip the enum declaration altogether, make it [ambient](http://www.typescriptlang.org/docs/handbook/enums.html#ambient-enums) as well:

